                    \end{aligned}</me>
                    </p><p>
                    <m>\therefore f_{x}^{\prime}(1,1)=2 </m>
                    </p><p>
                    由对称性可知<m>[f(1, y)]_{x}^{\prime}=y^{1+y}\left[\ln y+\frac{y+1}{y}\right]</m>
                    </p><p>
                    <m>f_{y}^{\prime}(1,2)=4(3+\ln 2)</m>
                </p>
            </answer>
        </exercise>

